        <h1>43,360 students await school closings decision</h1>
        <p>The Chicago Public Schools (CPS) has marked <strong>129 schools</strong> for possible closure based on utilization and performance. Closing a school is a very disruptive decision, affecting student outcomes, parental confidence, and neighborhood stability. 
<br />In addition to the data being used by CPS, this website provides additional data to help school leaders, parents and communities learn more about the schools being considered, and what neighborhood options will be available in case a school is closed.  </p>
        
